.SH NAME
shelly-theme-list - List available themes


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBshelly theme list [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
List all available color themes.

.PP
The CLI includes 280+ themes from bubbletint. Use --filter to search
for themes by name pattern (case-insensitive).

.PP
Use 'shelly theme set \&' to apply a theme.
Use 'shelly theme preview \&' to see a theme before applying.

.PP
Output is formatted as a table by default. Use -o json or -o yaml for
structured output suitable for scripting.

.PP
Columns: Theme (name), Current (checkmark if active)


.SH OPTIONS
\fB--filter\fP=""
	Filter themes by name pattern

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for list


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--config\fP=""
	Config file (default $HOME/.config/shelly/config.yaml)

.PP
